Maven:
  It is a build and Project Management Tool
  Pre-requisite Software:Java
  Default file name is:pom.xml
  It has a definite folder Structure when compared to Ant
  It has 3 Life Cycles:
     1.clean
        ->goal:clean
     2.site 
        ->goal:site
     3.default
        ->goals:
	    *validate
	    *compile
	    *test
	    *package
	    *install
	    *deploy

   It has 3 Repositories:
      1.Maven Local Repository
      2.Maven Central Repository
      3.Remote Repository


